    "title": "提多書 1:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "56001001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>知識……使人敬虔（knowledge … that leads to godliness(BSB)）：見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:11-Titus2:14\">2:11–14</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:3\">提前 6:3</a>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "56001001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "TIT 1:1",
          "end_ref": "56001001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "TIT 1:1"
        }
