    "reference_id": 25103,
    "title": "提多書 1:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "56001013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>這個見證是真的：見<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"25102\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">1:12的研讀註釋</span>。</p></li><li><p>在此，在真道上純全無疵（堅定）被定義為拒絕錯誤的教導（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:9\">1:9</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
