  {
    "content_id": 159045,
    "reference_id": 25104,
    "title": "提多書 1:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "56001014",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>猶太人荒渺的言語：見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:9\">3:9</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:4\">提摩太前書1:4</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:7\">4:7</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:4\">提摩太後書4:4</a>。</p></li><li><p>離棄真道：這是背道，而不僅僅是不信。背道是指某人放棄或拒絕他們原本所信的信仰。見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:6-1Tim1:7\">提摩太前書1:6–7</a>。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "56001014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "TIT 1:14",
          "end_ref": "56001014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "TIT 1:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 159047,
    "reference_id": 25106,
    "title": "提多書 1:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "56001015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:3-1Tim4:5\">提摩太前書4:3–5</a>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "56001015",
          "start_ref_usfm": "TIT 1:15",
          "end_ref": "56001015",
