  {
    "content_id": 159064,
    "reference_id": 25123,
    "title": "提多書 2:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "56002014",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>救恩塑造人渴望成為並有能力完成<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:2-Titus2:10\">2:2–10</a>中描述的善行。</p></li><li><p>祂捨了自己：另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:6\">提前2:6</a>。</p></li><li><p>要贖我們：見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:22\">加3:22</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:4-Gal4:5\">4:4–5</a>；參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod6:6-Exod6:8\">出6:6–8</a>。</p></li><li><p>「特作自己的子民」這個短語讓人想起以色列民的形成（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:5\">出19:5；</a><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:6\">申7:6</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut14:2\">14:2</a>）。那些跟隨基督的人現在是神的子民——祂的國度——聖靈引導他們遵守神的約。</p></li><li><p>熱心為善（totally committed to doing good deeds 〔BSB〕，完全致力於行善；字面意思是為善行而火熱）：見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:16\">多1:16</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:10\">弗2:10</a>。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "56002014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "TIT 2:14",
          "end_ref": "56002014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "TIT 2:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 159073,
    "reference_id": 25132,
    "title": "提多書 3:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "56003001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>保羅可能在告訴信徒要與不守紀律的普通大眾清楚區分開來。又或那些麻煩製造者（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:10-Titus1:15\">1:10–15</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:10\">3:10</a>）可能因為他們的錯誤教導而採取了不當的行為（這很可能是<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:1-1Tim2:7\">提摩太前書2:1–7</a>的情況）。</p></li><li><p>與作官的、掌權的之間的關係<em>，</em>見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:2\">提摩太前書二章2節</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:1-Rom13:7\">羅馬書十三章1至7節</a>。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "56003001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "TIT 3:1",
          "end_ref": "56003001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "TIT 3:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 159066,
    "reference_id": 25125,
    "title": "提多書 3:1–11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "56003001-56003011",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>經文繼續強調全備的教導（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:9\">1:9</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:1\">2:1</a>）。現在保羅轉而關注基督教群體如何與整個社會相處（參見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:2-1Tim2:4\">提摩太前書2:2–4</a>）。如同在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:1-Titus2:15\">提多書二章1至15節</a>中一樣，神對祂子民的指示（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:1-Titus3:2\">3:1–2</a>）是基於祂與他們的互動（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:3-Titus3:7\">3:3–7</a>；參<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"25119\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">研讀註釋2:11–15</span>）。接著，保羅指示提多避免無意義的爭論，並持守有益的教導（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:8-Titus3:11\">3:8–11</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "56003001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "TIT 3:1",
          "end_ref": "56003011",
          "end_ref_usfm": "TIT 3:11"
        }
      ],
      "resource": [
        {
          "reference_id": 25119,
          "content_id": 159060,
          "resource_code": "TyndaleStudyNotes",
          "label": "提多書 2:11-15",
          "language": "zht"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 159074,
    "reference_id": 25133,
    "title": "提多書 3:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "56003003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>我們應當謙卑並尊重每個人（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:2\">3:2</a>），尤其是因為神的慈愛和憐憫也曾臨到我們過去的光景（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:4\">3:4</a>；見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:1-Eph2:4\">弗2:1–4</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:8\">5:8</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:7\">西3:7</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:3\">彼前4:3</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "56003003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "TIT 3:3",
          "end_ref": "56003003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "TIT 3:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 159076,
    "reference_id": 25135,
    "title": "提多書 3:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "56003004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>我們應該以恩慈和慈愛對待我們的同胞，就像神對待我們一樣。神的救恩使這成為可能。</p></li><li><p>顯明（字面意思<em>出現</em>）：這個希臘詞與基督的來臨有關（也見於<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:11\">2:11</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:13\">13</a>；見<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"16535\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">提前6:14的研讀註釋</span>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "56003004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "TIT 3:4",
          "end_ref": "56003004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "TIT 3:4"
        }
