        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 159075,
    "reference_id": 25134,
    "title": "提多書 3:4–7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "56003004-56003007",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>這段經文可能是傳統教導的總結或引述（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:15\">提前1:15</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:5-1Tim2:6\">2:5–6</a>）。</p>",
