  {
    "content_id": 159077,
    "reference_id": 25136,
    "title": "提多書 3:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "56003005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>並不是因為……乃是：這裡所對比的是人們認為可以獲得救恩的行為與神的恩典（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:16\">加2:16</a>）。救恩是唯獨本乎神的憐憫，因著信心得以成就（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:8\">弗2:8</a>）。</p></li><li><p>重生的洗：見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:9\">結16:9</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:1-John3:15\">約3:1–15</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:26\">弗5:26</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:22\">來10:22</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:9\">彼後1:9</a>。</p></li><li><p>聖靈的更新：這表明完全脫離罪和死亡的生命，進入純潔的生命（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:2\">羅12:2</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:17\">林後5:17；</a><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:10\">西3:10</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "56003005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "TIT 3:5",
          "end_ref": "56003005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "TIT 3:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 159078,
    "reference_id": 25137,
    "title": "提多書 3:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "56003007",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>這節經文的前半部分總結了<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:4-Titus3:6\">三章4至6節</a>。後半部分提及了神所做之事的心意。</p></li><li><p>得稱為義（字面意思是<em>被稱為義</em>）：見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:20-Rom3:28\">羅3:20–28</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:16-Gal2:17\">加2:16–17</a>。</p></li><li><p>可以憑著永生的盼望成為後嗣：聖靈（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:5\">多3:5</a>）常與我們的後嗣身份聯繫在一起（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:15-Rom8:17\">羅8:15–17</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:9-1Cor6:11\">林前6:9–11</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:6-Gal4:7\">加4:6–7</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:13-Eph1:14\">弗1:13–14</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "56003007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "TIT 3:7",
          "end_ref": "56003007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "TIT 3:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 159079,
    "reference_id": 25138,
    "title": "提多書 3:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "56003008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>這話是可信的是指<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:4-Titus3:7\">3:4–7</a>（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:15\">提前1:15</a>）。</p>",
