  {
    "content_id": 159067,
    "reference_id": 25126,
    "title": "提多書 3:10–11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "56003010-56003011",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>分門結黨的人：這指的是那些好爭吵、難以糾正或改變的人（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:11\">1:11</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:13\">13</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "56003010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "TIT 3:10",
          "end_ref": "56003011",
          "end_ref_usfm": "TIT 3:11"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 159069,
    "reference_id": 25128,
    "title": "提多書 3:12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "56003012",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>顯然，亞提馬或推基古將接替提多留在克里特。由於推基古實際上是被派往以弗所（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:12\">提後4:12</a>），因此亞提馬才是那個去了克里特的人。</p></li><li><p>尼哥波里：有幾個城使用這個名字。這很可能是希臘半島（一塊四面環水、僅在一側與大陸相連的土地）西海岸的一個重要城市。保羅可能曾在這裡工作（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:19\">羅15:19</a>，其中提到保羅在更西邊的活動）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "56003012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "TIT 3:12",
          "end_ref": "56003012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "TIT 3:12"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 159068,
    "reference_id": 25127,
    "title": "提多書 3:12–15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "56003012-56003015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>這封信以消息（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:12\">3:12</a>）、最後的勸勉（或鼓勵）（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:13-Titus3:14\">3:13–14</a>）、問候和祝福（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:15\">3:15</a>）結束。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "56003012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "TIT 3:12",
          "end_ref": "56003015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "TIT 3:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 159070,
    "reference_id": 25129,
    "title": "提多書 3:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "56003013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>西納和亞波羅也參與傳揚耶穌的福音，他們可能是將這封信交給提多的人。</p></li><li><p>西納可能是一位羅馬律法專家或羅馬法學家（同樣的律師一詞也出現在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:30\">路7:30</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:25\">10:25</a>）。從他的希臘名字（意思是「宙斯的禮物」）推斷，他不太可能是猶太律法專家。</p></li><li><p>亞波羅可能是這些經文<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:24\">徒18:24</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:1\">19:1</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:12\">林前1:12</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:4-1Cor3:6\">3:4–6</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:22\">22</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:6\">4:6</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:12\">16:12</a>中提到的同一個人。</p></li><li><p>缺乏（<span>everything they need </span>〔<span>BSB</span>〕<span>，庇哩亞聖經譯為</span>他們所需的一切）：見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:2\">提前3:2</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:5-3John1:8\">約三1:5–8</a>；參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:24\">羅15:24</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:6\">林前16:6</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:11\">11</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:16\">林後1:16</a>。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "56003013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "TIT 3:13",
          "end_ref": "56003013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "TIT 3:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 159071,
    "reference_id": 25130,
    "title": "提多書 3:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "56003014",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>最後的勸勉與照顧西納和亞波羅的責任有關（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:13\">羅12:13；</a><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:28\">弗4:28</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:11\">帖前4:11</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:8\">提前5:8、</a><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:16\">16</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:18\">6:18</a>）。</p></li><li><p>我們的人（即基督的跟隨者）必須參與傳福音的生命事工，而不是參與假教師無益的空談推測。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "56003014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "TIT 3:14",
          "end_ref": "56003014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "TIT 3:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 159072,
    "reference_id": 25131,
    "title": "提多書 3:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "56003015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>你們眾人：這封信是寫給提多的（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:4\">1:4</a>），但整個教會都是這封信的讀者。</p>",
